

### Get All Products
GET http://localhost:8080/api/products


### Get product details
POST http://localhost:8080/api/products/details
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "productId": "69361d8964bcbb7c71862c70"
}

### Search products
GET http://localhost:8080/api/products/search?v=ap


### Get one product per category
GET http://localhost:8080/api/products/category-one


### Filter products by category and price order
POST http://localhost:8080/api/products/filter
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "category": ["airpode", "phone"],
  "sortBy": "asc"
}


### Update product
POST http://localhost:8080/api/products/update
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <admin_jwt_token>

{
  "_id": "69361d8964bcbb7c71862d05",
  "productName": "Marshall Kilburn II (Updated)",
  "sellingPrice": 259
}


### Upload product
POST http://localhost:8080/api/products/upload
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <admin_token_here>

{
  "productName": "Sony WH-1000XM5",
  "brandName": "Sony",
  "category": "headphones",
  "productImage": ["https://..."],
  "description": "High-end noise-cancelling headphones.",
  "price": 399,
  "sellingPrice": 349
}


PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/users/update
Content-Type: application/json
